Do you have broken power button? This app can save your phone! You can unlock screen by other keys and lock screen using widget.

Download from Market:
https://market.android.com/details?id=cz.destil.fixbrokenpb

Discussion:
https://groups.google.com/forum/?hl=en#!forum/fix-broken-power-button

This app is based on AnyUnlock, more here:
https://github.com/helloworld1/AnyUnlock
